                <h1>Understanding Feminism: Empowerment & Equality</h1>
                <p>Feminism advocates for the social, political, and economic equality of the genders. It challenges traditional gender roles, promotes women's rights, and strives for justice in various spheres of life. Understanding feminism is vital for fostering a balanced society, empowering individuals, and addressing systemic inequalities that persist today.</p>
